videos.headline: Henry Ellenson grabs the rebound and takes it all the way to the hole for a left-handed layup to get Marquette on the board

videos.description: 1H (9:02) WIS Vitto Brown made Jumper. Assisted by Bronson Koenig.
videos.headline: Bronson Koenig finds Vitto Brown wide open off of the screen for a two-point jumper

videos.description: 1H (8:00) MARQ Duane Wilson made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Jajuan Johnson.
videos.headline: Duane Wilson quickly gets set in transition for three

videos.description: 1H (7:18) WIS Vitto Brown made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Zak Showalter.
videos.headline: Vitto Brown is heating up, hits a three

videos.description: 1H (6:11) WIS Zak Showalter made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Bronson Koenig.
videos.headline: Zak Showalter gets his second three of the game

videos.description: 1H (2:53) MARQ Sandy Cohen III made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Henry Ellenson.
videos.headline: Henry Ellenson drives baseline but finds Sandy Cohen III wide open behind the arc for three

videos.description: 1H (0:49) MARQ Luke Fischer made Dunk. Assisted by Duane Wilson.
videos.headline: Luke Fischer cuts down the lane for a dunk
Ethan Happ shows off some fancy footwork, but Luke Fischer denies the layup to keep the Marquette lead for the first half

videos.description: 2H (18:11) MARQ Luke Fischer made Layup. Assisted by Sandy Cohen III.
videos.headline: Sandy Cohen III dishes to Luke Fischer over the Wisconsin defense for two

videos.description: 2H (12:27) MARQ Luke Fischer made Layup. Assisted by Henry Ellenson.
videos.headline: Henry Ellenson continues to be a playmaker, gets his fourth assist on a layup by Luke Fischer

videos.description: 2H (11:35) MARQ Henry Ellenson made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Jajuan Johnson.
videos.headline: Jajuan Johnson drives then finds Henry Ellenson, who has no problem getting it done all over the court

videos.description: 2H (10:01) WIS Bronson Koenig made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Nigel Hayes.
videos.headline: Bronson Koenig drains a three on cue

videos.description: 2H (6:13) WIS Nigel Hayes made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Zak Showalter.
videos.headline: Nigel Hayes hits a three to cut the lead to four points after a huge Wisconsin run

videos.description: 2H (5:42) MARQ Henry Ellenson made Two Point Tip Shot.
videos.headline: Henry Ellenson misses the layup, but grabs his own offensive board for a two-point putback and earns a double-double

videos.description: 2H (1:31) WIS Vitto Brown made Jumper. Assisted by Nigel Hayes.
videos.headline: Wisconsin comes back from a fourteen point deficit, Bronson Keonig and Vitto Brown come through with a pair of clutch jumpers to tie

videos.description: 2H (0:29) MARQ Luke Fischer made Two Point Tip Shot.
videos.headline: Luke Fischer gets the putback to put Marquette in the lead late in the game
Luke Fischer posts up big time to grab the offensive rebound off of a missed foul shot with five seconds left
